description:
Bobby talks about peeing through the fence in his backyard and peed on his dog’s ear. Caitlin asked why he couldn’t stop peeing. He said he can’t because it hurts. Food with Morgan2: McDonald’s New McFlurry with Caramel. Lunchbox shares his Top 3 Life Goals. We also debate whether or not we would retire right now.
